{
  "stem": "15396.3",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Because he would be so nice, and your coffee, you know.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And then he'd turn the knife.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "But boy, he sure had a-- he had a technique, let's put it that way.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, we were just being terribly careful about who came into this office where the refugee assistance was, being very careful and being sure that there were no passports or anything left around and the papers were there.",
      "word_count": 38
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And whenever I would go to send, you know, this rough section where you had to go to send the telegrams, had to pay for it in cash, and that was the trouble, was protecting the cash because it was right in the section where gangsters were, and I carried it in my sock all the time.",
      "word_count": 57
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "There were-- there were things that-- you learned fast, let's put it that way.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And as I say, adrenaline is a great help.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "It sort of-- when you're scared, you can do a lot of things that you can't do otherwise.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Nature did a lot for us, you know.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "In fact, never have.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Even today I doubt they do.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Oh, yes, by now they do because the-- the British published some things one time.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And also there have been a lot of things published since the Holocaust Museum opened.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But until that time, practically none of my friends knew anything about it.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "There's a big-- it varies greatly.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Some books have said 2,000.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Others say 2,400.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "The Holocaust Museum, I think, said 2,300 or something.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I would say that was pretty good.",
      "word_count": 7
    }
  ],
